"Beer" includes:
ale;
porter;
stout;
hard cider, as defined in Article 2B, § 1-102(a)(9-1) of the Code; and
alcoholic beverages that contain:

"Distilled spirits" includes:
alcohol;
brandy;
cordials;
gin;
liqueur;
rum;
vodka;
whiskey; and
solutions or mixtures of distilled spirits except fortified wines.

"Wine" includes:
carbonated, flavored, imitation, sparkling, or still wine;
champagne;
cider;
fortified wine;
perry;
sake; and
vermouth.
